      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i keep looking at the corner where his bed used to be and it just... it feels like the air is heavy. i don't even know why i'm getting up in the morning anymore. there's no reason to do anything if the only thing that made the day worth it is just gone. the house is too big and too empty. i just want the weight to stop.",
