      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just not just \"a tough time\" though. it feels like everything is just... finished. like the chapter is closed and there's nothing left to write. i look at the food in the fridge and i don't even see the point in eating. i look at the clock and it's just hours of existing for no reason. i feel so tired of just pretending that things will eventually get better when they clearly won't.",
