    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it really is suffocating. i'm just sitting here staring at the wall and thinking about how much energy it takes just to exist. it feels like i'm just performing a role that doesn't matter anymore. i look at the silence in this house and i just think... maybe it would be easier if it was just permanent. if the silence didn't have to be something i'm fighting against every single day.",
